    "DescriptionKey": "spacecollect_cargo_desc_H_01",
    "DisplayDescription": "RED WIND LINEHAUL\n'YOUR GOODS IN GOOD HANDS'\n----------------------------\n\nNeed an experienced pilot for this recovery contract. Unfortunately, the original delivery pilot was targeting by a group of outlaws. Thankfully, the client\u2019s packages are still sitting in their damaged ship located at <EM4>Glaciem Ring Wreck Site</EM4>.\n\nYou\u2019ll potentially need to <EM4>bring some backup</EM4> with you to ensure the successful collection and delivery of the packages.\n\nPACKAGES TO RECOVER\n     \u00b7 <EM4>4x [Item1]</EM4>\n\nDROP OFF LOCATION\n     \u00b7 Deliver to <EM4>[Destination|Target|Address]</EM4>\n\nConsidering the danger of this contract, we\u2019re willing to offer a slight pay increase as hazard pay.\n\nTAKE PRIDE IN YOUR WORK \u2013 Even as a contractor you are representing Red Wind Linehaul. Do not intentionally do anything to harm the company\u2019s reputation.",
